Srishti Singh is a faculty member in the Department of Civil Engineering at IIT Jammu. Designation: Faculty Member. Email: srishti.singh@iitjammu.ac.in. Education: 1. B.Sc (Hons) Physics, 2008-2011 (BHU);
2. M.Sc (Tech) Geophysics, 2011-2014 (BHU);
3. PhD, Earth Sciences, 2014-2020 (IISc Bangalore). Research areas: Geophysics, Solid Earth, Mantle Convection, Geodynamics, Plate Tectonics, Disaster Management.
